285
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:12,940
Tell me.

286
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:16,820
Do you know the Jiang sisters?

287
00:11:17,820 --> 00:11:19,180
No, they have nothing

288
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,420
