289
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:23,940
Do you know

290
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:24,980
Cao Xingyu then?

291
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:26,220
Yes,

292
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:27,540
sir.

293
